{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01Vyp64wwBz9mjJ72xE35A5y","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→/* Variables */\n     2→:root {\n     3→  --secondary-text-color: #f5f5f5;\n     4→\n     5→\n     6→  --primary-color: #FFA500;\n     7→  --primary-color-darker: #d48900;\n     8→  --primary-color-lighten: #f5ecda;\n     9→\n    10→  --secondary-color: #262626;\n    11→\n    12→  --background-panel-main-color: #262626;\n    13→}\n    14→\n    15→\n    16→body {\n    17→  height: 100vh;\n    18→  margin: 0;\n    19→}\n    20→\n    21→.full-page {\n    22→  height: 100vh;\n    23→}\n    24→\n    25→/*************************************\n    26→             Side panel style\n    27→ *************************************/\n    28→\n    29→.side-panel {\n    30→  background-color: var(--background-panel-main-color);\n    31→\n    32→  padding: 0;\n    33→  margin: 0;\n    34→}\n    35→\n    36→/*this is for overriding Primefaces' background and color */\n    37→.side-panel * {\n    38→  background-color: var(--background-panel-main-color);\n    39→  color: var(--secondary-text-color);\n    40→}\n    41→\n    42→.side-panel .side-panel-img {\n    43→  display: block;\n    44→\n    45→  width: 80%;\n    46→\n    47→  margin-left: auto;\n    48→  margin-right: auto;\n    49→\n    50→  margin-bottom: 50px;\n    51→}\n    52→\n    53→.side-panel>.menu-container {\n    54→  width: 100%;\n    55→  margin: 0;\n    56→\n    57→  font-size: 25px;\n    58→}\n    59→\n    60→.side-panel .menu-container .ui-menu {\n    61→  width: 100%;\n    62→  margin: 0;\n    63→  padding: 0;\n    64→  border: 0;\n    65→}\n    66→\n    67→.side-panel .menu-container .ui-menu .ui-menu-list .ui-menuitem {\n    68→  border-bottom: solid 2px var(--primary-color);\n    69→  margin: 0 0 10px 0;\n    70→  padding: 0 0 10px 0;\n    71→}\n    72→\n    73→.side-panel .menu-container .ui-menu .ui-menu-list .ui-menuitem:last-child {\n    74→  border-bottom: 0;\n    75→  margin-bottom: 0;\n    76→  padding-bottom: 0;\n    77→}\n    78→\n    79→.side-panel .menu-container .ui-menu .ui-state-hover {\n    80→  background: inherit;\n    81→  /* remove default Primefaces background on hover */\n    82→}\n    83→\n    84→.side-panel .menu-container .ui-menu .ui-state-hover span {\n    85→  color: orange;\n    86→}\n    87→\n    88→.side-panel .menu-footer {\n    89→  position: absolute;\n    90→  bottom: 0;\n    91→  width: inherit;\n    92→  margin-left: -0.5em;\n    93→}\n    94→\n    95→/*************************************\n    96→             Table style\n    97→ *************************************/\n    98→\n    99→.ui-datatable table {\n   100→  border-collapse: collapse;\n   101→  width: 100%;\n   102→  font-size: 0.9em;\n   103→}\n   104→\n   105→.ui-datatable .ui-datatable-header,\n   106→.ui-datatable .ui-datatable-footer {\n   107→  text-align: left;\n   108→  padding: 4px 10px;\n   109→  text-align-last: left;\n   110→}\n   111→\n   112→.ui-datatable .ui-datatable-header {\n   113→  background: var(--primary-color);\n   114→  color: #ffffff;\n   115→\n   116→  font-weight: bold;\n   117→  font-size: 2em;\n   118→\n   119→  border-bottom: 0 none;\n   120→}\n   121→\n   122→.ui-datatable .ui-datatable-footer {\n   123→  border-top: 0 none;\n   124→  background: var(--primary-color);\n   125→}\n   126→\n   127→.ui-datatable th.ui-state-default,\n   128→.ui-datatable tfoot td.ui-state-default {\n   129→  background: var(--primary-color);\n   130→\n   131→  color: #ffffff;\n   132→  text-align: center;\n   133→  font-weight: bold;\n   134→  font-size: 1.5em;\n   135→\n   136→  border-top: 0 none;\n   137→  border-right: 0 none;\n   138→  border-left: 0 none;\n   139→}\n   140→\n   141→.ui-datatable thead th,\n   142→.ui-datatable tbody td,\n   143→.ui-datatable tfoot td {\n   144→  padding: 4px 10px;\n   145→  white-space: pre-line;\n   146→}\n   147→\n   148→.ui-datatable thead th,\n   149→.ui-datatable tbody td,\n   150→.ui-datatable tfoot td,\n   151→.ui-datatable tfoot th {\n   152→  border: 0 none !important;\n   153→}\n   154→\n   155→.ui-datatable tbody>tr.ui-widget-content {\n   156→  border: 0 none;\n   157→}\n   158→\n   159→.ui-datatable-odd {\n   160→  background-color: var(--primary-color-lighten);\n   161→}\n   162→\n   163→/*************************************\n   164→             Calendar style\n   165→ *************************************/\n   166→.ui-datepicker .ui-datepicker-header,\n   167→.ui-datepicker .ui-timepicker-div>.ui-widget-header {\n   168→  background: var(--background-panel-main-color);\n   169→  background: -webkit-linear-gradient(top, var(--background-panel-main-color) 0, #474a4b 100%);\n   170→\n   171→  box-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15) inset;\n   172→  border-radius: 0;\n   173→}\n   174→\n   175→.ui-datepicker .ui-datepicker-header,\n   176→.ui-datepicker .ui-timepicker-div>.ui-widget-header {\n   177→  border: 1px solid #3b3e40;\n   178→}\n   179→\n   180→.ui-datepicker th {\n   181→  color: #e8e9ea !important;\n   182→\n   183→  background: -webkit-gradient(linear, left top, left bottom, color-stop(0, #474a4b), color-stop(100%, #5b5e5e));\n   184→\n   185→  text-shadow: 0 -1px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);\n   186→  border: none !important;\n   187→}\n   188→\n   189→.ui-datepicker-current-day a {\n   190→  background: var(--primary-color) !important;\n   191→  color: #fff !important;\n   192→}\n   193→\n   194→/*************************************\n   195→             Components style\n   196→ *************************************/\n   197→\n   198→.ui-button,\n   199→button.ui-button.ui-state-default,\n   200→.ui-button.ui-state-default {\n   201→  background-color: var(--primary-color);\n   202→  border: 1px solid var(--primary-color-darker);\n   203→\n   204→  color: var(--secondary-text-color);\n   205→\n   206→}\n   207→\n   208→.ui-state-highlight,\n   209→.ui-widget-content .ui-state-highlight,\n   210→.ui-widget-header .ui-state-highlight {\n   211→  background: var(--primary-color-darker);\n   212→  color: var(--secondary-text-color);\n   213→}\n   214→\n   215→.ui-inputfield {\n   216→  border-width: 0 0 2px;\n   217→  border-color: var(--secondary-color)\n   218→}\n   219→\n   220→.ui-inputfield.ui-state-focus {\n   221→  outline: 0 none;\n   222→  box-shadow: none;\n   223→  border-color: var(--primary-color);\n   224→}\n   225→\n   226→/*************************************\n   227→             Timeline style\n   228→ *************************************/\n   229→\n   230→.ok-timeline-event {\n   231→  border: #90ee90;\n   232→  background: #818181 none !important;\n   233→  color: #ffffff !important;\n   234→}\n   235→\n   236→.error-timeline-event {\n   237→  border: #cd5c5c;\n   238→  background: #d26161 none !important;\n   239→  color: #ffffff !important;\n   240→}\n   241→\n   242→/*************************************\n   243→             Wizard style\n   244→ *************************************/\n   245→\n   246→.ui-wizard-step-titles {\n   247→  display: flex;\n   248→  align-items: center;\n   249→  justify-content: center;\n   250→\n   251→  width: 100%;\n   252→}\n   253→\n   254→.ui-wizard-step-titles::before {\n   255→  content: ' ';\n   256→  border-top: 1px solid black;\n   257→  width: 100%;\n   258→  left: 0;\n   259→  display: block;\n   260→  position: absolute;\n   261→  z-index: -100;\n   262→}\n   263→\n   264→.ui-wizard-step-title::before {\n   265→  content: '';\n   266→  display: inline-block;\n   267→  width: 15px;\n   268→  height: 15px;\n   269→  -moz-border-radius: 7.5px;\n   270→  -webkit-border-radius: 7.5px;\n   271→  border-radius: 7.5px;\n   272→  background-color: var(--background-panel-main-color);\n   273→  padding: 1px;\n   274→  margin: 10px;\n   275→}\n   276→\n   277→.ui-wizard-step-title {\n   278→  font-size: 0 !important;\n   279→  background: none;\n   280→  border: none;\n   281→}\n   282→\n   283→.ui-wizard-step-title.ui-state-highlight::before {\n   284→  background-color: var(--primary-color);\n   285→}\n   286→\n   287→iframe {\n   288→  border: none;\n   289→}\n   290→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_015SsvXr6a7XzhL3X8fB5Ba7","session_id":"300f1a06-b6cf-43f1-b117-9879dd779de7","uuid":"ff77be0f-24bd-4bb4-a8bb-4dc67272f668"}
