RouteCandidate.java, Location.java, Leg.java (81 lines), CargoStatus.java (64 lines), CargoRoute.java (114 lines)\n- Web Controllers: ChangeArrivalDeadline.java, CargoDetails.java, Booking.java (167 lines), Track.java, ListCargo.java, ItinerarySelection.java, ChangeDestination.java (88 lines), ChangeArrivalDeadlineDialog.java, ChangeDestinationDialog.java\n- SSE: RealtimeCargoTrackingViewAdapter.java (86 lines), LocationViewAdapter.java, RealtimeCargoTrackingService.java (75 lines)\n- Assemblers: ItineraryCandidateDtoAssembler.java (64 lines), LocationDtoAssembler.java, TrackingEventsDtoAssembler.java (52 lines), CargoStatusDtoAssembler.java (97 lines), CargoRouteDtoAssembler.java (46 lines)\n- Handling: HandlingEventRegistrationAttempt.java (83 lines), EventLogger.java (214 lines)\n- File Handling: UploadDirectoryScanner.java, LineParseExceptionListener.java (52 lines), FileProcessorJobListener.java, EventLineParseException.java, EventItemWriter.java (73 lines), EventFilesCheckpoint.java, EventItemReader.java (155 lines)\n\n### Pathfinder Module (4 files)\n\nThese files implement the routing/pathfinding functionality:\n- GraphDao.java (40 lines) - Data access for graph traversal\n- TransitPath.java (35 lines) - Represents a transit path\n- TransitEdge.java (89 lines) - Represents an edge in the path\n- GraphTraversalService.java (100 lines) - REST service for finding shortest paths\n\nAll files have been successfully read with their complete contents. This is a comprehensive Jakarta EE application implementing a Domain-Driven Design (DDD) cargo tracker system with layers for application services, domain model, infrastructure, and user interfaces."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"300f1a06-b6cf-43f1-b117-9879dd779de7","uuid":"530257b4-ef24-4f79-94f8-a140075a860d"}
