{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_012KYWcuwbT5pBT5BSmLhFeY","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! All migrations have been completed successfully. Let me create a summary of all the changes made:\n\n## Migration Summary\n\nI have successfully migrated all 13 infrastructure layer Java files from Jakarta EE to Quarkus. Here's what was changed:\n\n### Files Updated:\n\n#### 1. **LoggerProducer.java** (`infrastructure/logging/`)\n- **Path**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/logging/LoggerProducer.java`\n- Changed `javax.*` imports to `jakarta.*`\n- Removed `Serializable` interface\n- Removed `serialVersionUID`\n\n#### 2. **CargoUpdated.java** (`infrastructure/events/cdi/`)\n- **Path**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/events/cdi/CargoUpdated.java`\n- Changed `javax.inject.Qualifier` to `jakarta.inject.Qualifier`\n\n#### 3. **JpaCargoRepository.java** (`infrastructure/persistence/jpa/`)\n- **Path**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/persistence/jpa/JpaCargoRepository.java`\n- Changed all `javax.*` imports to `jakarta.*`\n- Removed `Serializable` interface\n- Replaced `@PersistenceContext` with `@Inject` for EntityManager\n- Removed `serialVersionUID`\n\n#### 4. **JpaVoyageRepository.java** (`infrastructure/persistence/jpa/`)\n- **Path**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/persistence/jpa/JpaVoyageRepo