onAttemptConsumer.java** (`infrastructure/messaging/jms/`)\n- **Path**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/jms/HandlingEventRegistrationAttemptConsumer.java`\n- Replaced `@MessageDriven` with `@ApplicationScoped`\n- Removed `MessageListener` interface\n- Replaced `onMessage(Message)` with `onHandlingEventRegistrationAttempt(@ObservesAsync HandlingEventRegistrationAttempt)`\n- Simplified error handling (removed RuntimeException throw)\n\n#### 13. **ExternalRoutingService.java** (`infrastructure/routing/`)\n- **Path**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/routing/ExternalRoutingService.java`\n- Changed all `javax.*` imports to `jakarta.*`\n- Replaced `@Stateless` with `@ApplicationScoped` and `@Transactional`\n- Replaced `@Resource(lookup = \"java:app/configuration/GraphTraversalUrl\")` with `@ConfigProperty(name = \"app.graph-traversal-url\")`\n- Changed from JNDI resource lookup to MicroProfile Config\n\n### Key Migration Patterns:\n\n1. **Namespace Migration**: All `javax.*` imports changed to `jakarta.*`\n2. **EntityManager Injection**: `@PersistenceContext` replaced with `@Inject`\n3. **Configuration**: `@Resource` JNDI lookup replaced with `@ConfigProperty` (MicroProfile Config)\n4. **Messaging**: JMS `@MessageDriven` beans replaced with CDI `@ObservesAsync` event observers\n5. **Scope**: `@Stateless` EJBs replaced with `@ApplicationScoped` CDI beans\n6. **Serialization**: Removed `Serializable` interface and `serialVersionUID` (not needed in Quarkus)\n\nAll files have been successfully migrated and are now Quarkus-compatible!"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"300f1a06-b6cf-43f1-b117-9879dd779de7","uuid":"6a569bbc-ad40-46b5-bad5-7a85f63af512"}
