{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01EsCGZ6VRQRK8LC9rGhKXAy","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent! All the migrations have been completed successfully. Let me create a summary of all the changes made:\n\n## Migration Summary\n\nI have successfully migrated all Java application service files from Jakarta EE to Quarkus in the `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/` directory.\n\n### Files Modified:\n\n#### 1. **RestConfiguration.java**\n- **Location**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/util/RestConfiguration.java`\n- **Changes**: \n  - Replaced `javax.ws.rs.*` with `jakarta.ws.rs.*`\n  - Removed GlassFish-specific ServerProperties configuration\n  - Simplified to a clean Quarkus REST configuration with `@ApplicationPath(\"/rest\")`\n\n#### 2. **SampleDataGenerator.java**\n- **Location**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/util/SampleDataGenerator.java`\n- **Changes**:\n  - Replaced `@Singleton` and `@Startup` with `@ApplicationScoped`\n  - Replaced `@PostConstruct` with `@Observes StartupEvent` pattern\n  - Replaced `@PersistenceContext` with `@Inject` for EntityManager\n  - Added `@Transactional` annotation\n  - Updated all javax imports to jakarta imports\n\n#### 3. **ApplicationSettings.java**\n- **Location**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/util/ApplicationSettings.java`\n- **Changes**: Replaced `javax.persistence.*` with `jakarta.persistence.*`\n\n#### 4. **DateConverter.java**\n- **Location**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/util/DateConverter.java`\n- **Changes**: No changes needed (no javax imports)\n\n#### 5. **BookingService.java**\n- **Location**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/BookingService.java`\n- **Changes**: Replaced `javax.validation.*` with `jakarta.validation.*`\n\n#### 6. **CargoInspectionService.java**\n- **Location**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/CargoInspectionService.java`\n- **Changes**: Replaced `javax.validation.*` with `jakarta.validation.*`\n\n#### 7. **HandlingEventService.java**\n- **Location**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/HandlingEventService.java`\n- **Changes**: Replaced `javax.validation.*` with `jakarta.validation.*`\n\n#### 8. **ApplicationEvents.java**\n- **Location**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/ApplicationEvents.java`\n- **Changes**: No changes needed (no javax imports)\n\n#### 9. **DefaultBookingService.java**\n- **Location**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/internal/DefaultBookingService.java`\n- **Changes**:\n  - Removed `@Stateless` EJB annotation\n  - Added `@ApplicationScoped` and `@Transactional` annotations\n  - Replaced `javax.ejb.*` with jakarta equivalents\n  - Replaced `javax.inject.Inject` with `jakarta.inject.Inject`\n\n#### 10. **DefaultCargoInspectionService.java**\n- **Location**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/internal/DefaultCargoInspectionService.java`\n- **Changes**:\n  - Removed `@Stateless` EJB annotation\n  - Added `@ApplicationScoped` and `@Transactional` annotations\n  - Replaced `javax.ejb.*` with jakarta equivalents\n  - Replaced `javax.inject.Inject` with `jakarta.inject.Inject`\n\n#### 11. **DefaultHandlingEventService.java**\n- **Location**: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/internal/DefaultHandlingEventService.java`\n- **Changes**:\n  - Removed `@Stateless` EJB annotation\n  - Added `@ApplicationScoped` and `@Transactional` annotations\n  - Replaced `javax.ejb.*` with jakarta equivalents\n  - Replaced `javax.inject.Inject` with `jakarta.inject.Inject`\n\n### Key Migration Patterns Applied:\n\n1. **Namespace Migration**: All `javax.*` imports replaced with `jakarta.*`\n2. **EJB to CDI**: Replaced `@Stateless` with `@ApplicationScoped` and `@Transactional`\n3. **Startup Pattern**: Changed from `@Singleton/@Startup/@PostConstruct` to `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Observes StartupEvent`\n4. **Entity Manager Injection**: Changed from `@PersistenceContext` to `@Inject EntityManager`\n5. **REST Configuration**: Simplified to Quarkus-compatible configuration without GlassFish-specific properties\n\nAll files have been successfully migrated and are now compatible with Quarkus framework while maintaining the same business logic and functionality."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id